metrics.visualTitle: Sum of SO2, Sum of SO2, Sum of SO2, Sum of SO2 and Sum of SO2 by Year, Quarter, Month and Day

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({2012}, 'LocalDateTable_7c484106-a9f6-4e66-ac36-8b6692c5788c'[Year])

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'LocalDateTable_7c484106-a9f6-4e66-ac36-8b6692c5788c'[Year],
			'LocalDateTable_7c484106-a9f6-4e66-ac36-8b6692c5788c'[Quarter],
			'LocalDateTable_7c484106-a9f6-4e66-ac36-8b6692c5788c'[QuarterNo],
			'LocalDateTable_7c484106-a9f6-4e66-ac36-8b6692c5788c'[Month],
			'LocalDateTable_7c484106-a9f6-4e66-ac36-8b6692c5788c'[MonthNo],
			'LocalDateTable_7c484106-a9f6-4e66-ac36-8b6692c5788c'[Day],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			"SumSO2", CALCULATE(SUM('STN1'[SO2])),
			"STN2SumSO2", IGNORE(CALCULATE(SUM('STN2'[SO2]))),
			"STN3SumSO2", IGNORE(CALCULATE(SUM('STN3'[SO2]))),
			"STN4SumSO2", IGNORE(CALCULATE(SUM('STN4'[SO2]))),
			"STN5SumSO2", IGNORE(CALCULATE(SUM('STN5'[SO2]))),
			"MinDate", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MIN('LocalDateTable_7c484106-a9f6-4e66-ac36-8b6692c5788c'[Date])))
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
		SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(
			3500,
			__DS0Core,
			[MinDate],
			[SumSO2],
			[STN2SumSO2],
			[STN3SumSO2],
			[STN4SumSO2],
			[STN5SumSO2],
			350,
			,
			ALPHABETICAL,
			ASC,
			105000,
			60
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
	"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyBinnedSample

ORDER BY
	'LocalDateTable_7c484106-a9f6-4e66-ac36-8b6692c5788c'[Year],
	'LocalDateTable_7c484106-a9f6-4e66-ac36-8b6692c5788c'[QuarterNo],
	'LocalDateTable_7c484106-a9f6-4e66-ac36-8b6692c5788c'[Quarter],
